creator: AI Gahaku
descriptionHtml:
✨Join over 4 million users in creating stunning dot art with the power of AI✨
PixelMe is the go-to app for beginners and experts alike, designed for a seamless drawing experience on your smartphone.

🎨AI-assisted art creation🎨
With PixelMe's AI support, generate a variety of sketches based on your desired image, or create one from a photo taken by your camera or smartphone. Easily create characters, landscapes, items, and more, even if you're a beginner.

📱Stress-free drawing on your smartphone📱
No more hiding parts of your drawing with your finger! Just move the cursor to the desired location and press the DRAW button to place a dot. PixelMe makes it a breeze to create dot art on your smartphone.

🎮Great for game development & web design🎮
Create unique dot art with AI support and enhance your game or website designs. PixelMe takes your projects to the next level.

📿Design bead art patterns with ease📿
Easily create your own bead art designs with PixelMe. The AI support helps bring your ideas to life, resulting in amazing bead art creations.

🌟Show off your individuality on social media & share effortlessly🌟
Use PixelMe-created dot art in your profile pictures or posts to express your unique style. Share with friends and followers to spark conversations. The in-app sharing feature makes it easy to post your creations on social media.

🏆Over 4 million users endorse PixelMe🏆
"This is amazing. I use it to make oerler bead patterns and it's definitely worth the subscription!!!"
"just a few edits & the result are amazing"
PixelMe is highly rated by more than 4 million users. Try it out for yourself!

✍Recommended for designers & illustrators✍
PixelMe is not just for beginners; it's perfect for designers and illustrators too. Create your own dot art masterpieces with AI support and add them to your portfolio.

Download PixelMe now and expand your world of dot art!

creator: AI Gahaku
descriptionHtml:
Transform Your Photos into Stunning Pixel Art with PixelMe – Your Ultimate Pixel Art Studio!

Ever dreamed of turning your photos into unique pixel art creations? With PixelMe, unleash your creativity by transforming any picture - whether it’s your face, pets, landscapes, or any scene - into distinctive 8-bit style artwork. Powered by advanced AI, PixelMe offers you the magical experience of pixelating images effortlessly, while giving you the freedom to enhance and personalize each piece with our intuitive editor.

Why Choose PixelMe for Your Pixel Art Journey?

AI-Powered Pixelation: Instantly convert your photos into pixel art with our sophisticated AI. Whether it’s a portrait, an animal, or a scenic view, PixelMe breathes life into your images with a nostalgic, 8-bit twist.
Hands-On Customization: Not entirely satisfied with the AI's creation? Dive in with PixelMe’s editing options - adjust hues, brightness, and contrast to perfection, or manually refine details to your taste.
Versatile Pixel Art Toolkit: From beginners to seasoned artists, PixelMe caters to all. Use our pixel art maker to start from scratch or add your personal touch to AI-generated artworks.
Be Your Own Pixel Artist: Embrace the full spectrum of pixel art with tools designed for both novices and experts. Draw, dot, or sprite your way to stunning creations using our user-friendly interface.
Share Your Masterpieces: Integrated seamlessly with social platforms, PixelMe makes it easy to showcase your pixel art. Share your work and inspire others in the pixel art community!
Endless Creativity with Various Themes: Whether you’re into game design, dotpict art, or classic studio creations, our app supports a wide range of pixel art styles, including beads, resprite, pixilart, and more.
Join the PixelMe community now and transform everyday photos into pixel-perfect artworks. Whether you're reminiscing in the retro charm of 8-bit graphics or exploring the artistic possibilities of pixaki, PixelMe is your companion on this colorful journey.

Privacy & Support:
We respect your privacy. For more details, please visit our Privacy Policy: https://pixel-me.tokyo/en/privacy.

PixelMe is not just a game maker or a simple photo editor; it's a gateway to a world where your photos become the canvas for pixel artistry. Download PixelMe now and start your pixel art adventure today!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Fixed an issue where the file creation date was incorrect when saving images.
